Se the nodette's selected sinal estiver verde, coloque the hilite color into the fill.
Draw the roundy box with the border e the fill.
Adicione 1/24 inch to the roundy box's left.
Draw the nodette's directory in the roundy box with the gray color e the default font e "left".
Coloque the nodette's designator into um designator.
Se the nodette's kind for "disk", obtenha um description por the nodette's path.
Se the nodette's kind for "disk", posponha " (" then the description then ")" to the designator.
\  if the nodette's kind for "disk", obtenha um drive kind por the nodette's path.
\  if the nodette's kind for "disk", posponha " (" then the drive kind then ")" to the designator.
\  if the nodette's kind for "disk", obtenha um drive name por the nodette's path.
\  if the nodette's kind for "disk", posponha " (" then the drive name then ")" to the designator.
Obtenha um width usando the nodette's directory e the memory canvas e the default font.
