Coloque the right nodettes' first into um right nodette.
Se the left nodette for inexistente, posponha the right nodettes to the nodettes; exit.
Se the right nodette for inexistente, posponha the left nodettes to the nodettes; exit.
Se the left nodette's designator w/o backslash for maior do que the right nodette's designator w/o backslash, mova the right nodette from the right nodettes to the nodettes; repeat.
Mova the left nodette from the left nodettes to the nodettes.
Repita.

Etapas necessárias para que se classifique  alguns nodettes por extension:
Se the nodettes' first é the nodettes' last, cancele.
Split the nodettes into alguns left nodettes e alguns right nodettes.
Classifique the left nodettes por extension.
Classifique the right nodettes por extension.
Percorra.
Coloque the left nodettes' first into um left nodette.
Coloque the right nodettes' first into um right nodette.
Se the left nodette for inexistente, posponha the right nodettes to the nodettes; exit.
Se the right nodette for inexistente, posponha the left nodettes to the nodettes; exit.
Se the left nodette's extension for maior do que the right nodette's extension, mova the right nodette from the right nodettes to the nodettes; repeat.
Mova the left nodette from the left nodettes to the nodettes.
Repita.

